name: 2024 12th International Conference on Civil Engineering
content: Paper Publishing: For papers submitted to ICCEN 2024, accepted papers will be recommended to be published in the International Journal of Structural and Civil Engineering Research (IJSCER, ISSN: 2319-6009), and will be included in New Jour (Electronic Journals & Newsletters), Open J-Gate, Index Copernicus International, Indian Science, Research BIB Japan.
